			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Was just reading the postings on this item and thought i should let you all know the scoope.  <BR>
Quest starts in Temple of Solusek Ro.<BR>
You need 3 Runes of Scale.<BR>
1 from Firescale Croc in Lavastorm<BR>
2 from Deepwater Croc in Oasis of Marr<BR>
3 from Saltwater Croc in Upper Guk.<BR>
<BR>
Then you need to find a Lizardscale Cloak and take them all  to the Temple of Solusek Ro and give them to the NPC that gave you the quest.<BR>
<BR>
I have Rune from Deepwater Croc and the Lizard Cloak, but spent 3 hours looking for a Firescale croc and was unable to locate one.  My suggestion is to take a druid or a ranger with tracking with you.<BR>
<BR>
Good luck to you all on this.<BR>
<BR>
Udayil Barrison'del'indhet
